      参数类型为loadCNF的cotrollers中的构造器 
      构造器和说明
      loadWebSource(WebScraping webSp, loadCNF cnf)
      a constructor for load information from Internet need to load configuration file to know the path of resource and model of reading.
      QueryDatabase(loadCNF cnf)
      a constructor for load information from a configuration file the configuration file contains the model(csv,db,net) of loading data and the path of file which stores data

      a construcotr to creat a object.
